<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>+Pulse - Master Your Insurance Journey</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Silkscreen:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffcdd6 0%, #651fab 100%);
            color: #333;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 44, 88, 0.1) 0%, rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.1) 100%);
        }

        .hero-content {
            max-width: 800px;
            z-index: 2;
            position: relative;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-family: 'Silkscreen', monospace;
            font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 5rem);
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            line-height: 1.1;
        }

        .hero-subtitle {
            font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 3vw, 1.8rem);
            color: #f8f9fa;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        .hero-description {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #e9ecef;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }

        .cta-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff2c58 0%, #ff6b35 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(255, 44, 88, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            color: white;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 35px rgba(255, 44, 88, 0.4);
            color: white;
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            color: white;
        }

        /* Features Section */
        .features {
            padding: 5rem 0;
            background: #fff;
        }

        .features h2 {
            text-align: center;
            font-family: 'Silkscreen', monospace;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .features-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            border: 2px solid #f8f9fa;
        }

        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }

        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            display: block;
        }

        .feature-card h3 {
            font-family: 'Silkscreen', monospace;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            color: #ff2c58;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .feature-card p {
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Stats Section */
        .stats {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff2c58 0%, #ff6b35 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 4rem 0;
        }

        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .stat-item h3 {
            font-family: 'Silkscreen', monospace;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .stat-item p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        /* CTA Section */
        .final-cta {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 5rem 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .final-cta h2 {
            font-family: 'Silkscreen', monospace;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .final-cta p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .cta-buttons {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }
            
            .btn-primary, .btn-secondary {
                width: 100%;
                max-width: 300px;
                justify-content: center;
            }
            
            .features-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            
            .stats-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            }
        }

        /* Animations */
        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .hero-content > * {
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out forwards;
        }

        .hero-subtitle {
            animation-delay: 0.2s;
        }

        .hero-description {
            animation-delay: 0.4s;
        }

        .cta-buttons {
            animation-delay: 0.6s;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <%- include('partials/navbar.ejs') %>
    </header>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <h1>+PULSE</h1>
                <p class="hero-subtitle">Master Your Integrated Shield Plan Journey</p>
                <p class="hero-description">
                    Empowering young Singaporeans aged 21-34 with the knowledge and tools to make informed decisions about Integrated Shield Plans. Learn through interactive modules, play engaging games, and win rewards while mastering your healthcare insurance journey.
                </p>
                <div class="cta-buttons">
                    <a href="/education/modules" class="btn-primary">
                        🎓 Start Learning
                    </a>
                    <a href="/ai-comparison" class="btn-secondary">
                        🔍 Compare Plans
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Features Section -->
    <section class="features">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Why Choose +Pulse?</h2>
            <div class="features-grid">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <span class="feature-icon">🎯</span>
                    <h3>Targeted Learning</h3>
                    <p>Specially designed for young adults in Singapore who need to understand Integrated Shield Plans for better healthcare decisions.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <span class="feature-icon">🎮</span>
                    <h3>Gamified Experience</h3>
                    <p>Learn through interactive modules, quizzes, and AI-powered games that make insurance education engaging and fun.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <span class="feature-icon">🏆</span>
                    <h3>Earn Rewards</h3>
                    <p>Complete modules and quizzes to earn tokens that can be redeemed for exciting rewards in our marketplace.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <span class="feature-icon">🤖</span>
                    <h3>AI-Powered Tools</h3>
                    <p>Use our intelligent comparison tool to analyze different insurance plans and find the best fit for your needs.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <span class="feature-icon">📊</span>
                    <h3>Track Progress</h3>
                    <p>Monitor your learning journey with detailed progress tracking and personalized recommendations.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <span class="feature-icon">🛡️</span>
                    <h3>Expert Content</h3>
                    <p>Access curated content about Integrated Shield Plans, riders, and healthcare coverage in Singapore.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Stats Section -->
    <section class="stats">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="stats-grid">
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <h3>21-34</h3>
                    <p>Target Age Group</p>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <h3>100%</h3>
                    <p>Interactive Learning</p>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <h3>🇸🇬</h3>
                    <p>Made for Singapore</p>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <h3>Free</h3>
                    <p>Always Accessible</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Final CTA Section -->
    <section class="final-cta">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Ready to Take Control?</h2>
            <p>
                Don't let insurance decisions overwhelm you. Join +Pulse today and transform complex insurance concepts into simple, actionable knowledge that will serve you for life.
            </p>
            <a href="/register" class="btn-primary">
                🚀 Get Started Free
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>
</body>

</html>
